  "name": "Endure Death's Touch",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wearing medium or heavy armor in which you have expert proficiency.</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> An undead hits you with an unarmed attack.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your conviction redirects the undead's attack through your armor and then harmlessly away. You gain resistance 5 to physical damage and resistance 10 to negative damage against the triggering attack. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus on any saving throws against effects from the undead's natural attack; if you succeed at the saving throw, you get a critical success instead.</p>"
